=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hottoyssecretbase/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hottoys.com.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hottoys.com.hk%2F&d=1qTZy9M3gJMnvKVqcUQz3qNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=9db61d24\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hottoys.com.hk/</a><br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">墮坑前請先睇下自己銀包<br />\n夠錢唔好諗 即刻訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">HOT TOYS 原價表 COPY FROM FACEBOOK &rdquo;Hottoys 香港交流區&ldquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/fsRVRm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FfsRVRm&d=1qTZy9M3gJMnvKVqcUQz3qNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=c563cfa4\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/fsRVRm</a></span></div>"},{"pid":"44c1e87681fa100dfec0358e33fe86b406600414","tid":895939,"uid":113059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T15:00:00.000Z","msg":"======================================================================<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Q&amp;A</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 交收個陣有乜要注意呀 好驚有問題呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : IM系列最緊要CHECK下齊唔齊件(參考 威威夏威夷 巴打), 如果店主話自己只CHECK件無玩過正常IM上面都有層膠.<br />\n除左iron man diecast全部 以及dx所有系列, 其他都係無啡盒既. 交收訂單要注意最好上去加名,小心比人用報失拎左你件野. 加左名既話就算佢要報失都要兩個人一齊上去先拎到貨 同埋一定要KEEP買賣既RECORD.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 點解我上網睇隻iron man會咁平 46賣1000幾我係咪執到好野 ？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 咁你就要睇清楚你個隻係咪powerpose ,pps既價錢同盒都同⅙唔同，一般都平過⅙好多<br />\n根據9巴提供<br />\n1/4 無合金<br />\n1/6 會有膠版 <br />\ndiecast即係合金<br />\n(1-7合金暫時出左mk2 3 4 5 6 ,42打後都係合金)<br />\npps(42 46 47 hb2.0)<br />\n再次鳴謝 9_Januzaj巴打提供<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :想知道ht係咪同款通常唔會再開訂?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :係 截左就無得訂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :截左訂點算?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :只可以等現貨(好大機會無)或同其他人收(E.g:facebook group, Yahoo Bid)<br />\n20樓係訂同派貨<br />\n2樓 Toyhunter就散死貨同少量正野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :幾時截訂?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :唔知幾時截訂 截訂就多數2個月之後 每隻唔同<br />\n唔想食炒價就訂定 慢慢等 PS:衡量自己財政<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :啲手好難換 點算?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :吹風筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :邊隻邊隻炒唔炒得起?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :關你鬼事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有愛就訂 考慮緊嘅就睇多幾次套戲 唔係唔訂下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :點樣可以保養隻HOT TOYS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 以下轉自網上<br />\n不要被太陽長時間直射<br />\n合金長時間在太陽下爆曬，高溫會導致顏色變淺，表面油漆可能會起泡及龜烈，嚴重影響figures的外觀。要留意，就算放到飾櫃但長時間用射燈照視，都可能會導致上述問題。<br />\n避免在雙手不乾淨時觸碰<br />\n手上的汗水與油份很容易黏在合金表面，久而久之就會氧化成一層白白的薄膜，所以接觸figures前最好先將雙手清潔乾淨。<br />\n留意溫度及濕度<br />\n香港天氣潮濕，所以要十分留意家中的濕度，因為太潮濕會引致生銹;至於溫度方面，太大的溫差會導致熱漲冷縮，令hot toys變得脆弱。所以將空間保持乾爽對保存hot Toys很重要。<br />\n放入玻璃櫃display , 得閒用除塵帚 掃幾下<br />\nIM電池保養方法：<br />\nim果d版電仔唔好長時間放係本體入面<br />\n玩完 着完燈 j完好拎哂d電出黎<br />\n因為d版電仔放係本體入面耐左會發漲<br />\n最後會爆漿 會損壞im d電路<br />\n大家玩im開心之餘記得留意下電池咩情況 （BY 舒洛特 巴打）<br />\n======================================================================"},{"pid":"0273598d0306f21e43f3b85588cfc8e351d1873b","tid":895939,"uid":113059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T15:00:42.000Z","msg":"======================================================================<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 毒圖時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/153636_2c97051286580b742a428f816691b07a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F153636_2c97051286580b742a428f816691b07a.png&h=1acebab4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/153640_c09924e055337313a83f1ea689440879.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F153640_c09924e055337313a83f1ea689440879.png&h=f3ddd0db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/153646_0ecdc29b1419f3b8027e71d31edd3c51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F153646_0ecdc29b1419f3b8027e71d31edd3c51.jpg&h=5efe3aa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/up